textfsm_template:
Value LOGICAL_SYSTEM (\S+)
Value INTERFACE (\S+)
Value IP_ADDRESS (\S+)
Value ADMIN (\S+)
Value LINK (\S+)
Value PROTOCOL (\S+)

Start
  ^\s*Interface\s+IP-Address\s+Admin\s+Link\s+Protocol\s*$$
  ^\s*${LOGICAL_SYSTEM}\s*$$ -> LogicalSystem
  ^\s*${INTERFACE}\s+${IP_ADDRESS}\s+${ADMIN}\s+${LINK}\s+${PROTOCOL}\s*$$ -> Record

LogicalSystem
  ^\s*${LOGICAL_SYSTEM}\s*$$
  ^\s*${INTERFACE}\s+${IP_ADDRESS}\s+${ADMIN}\s+${LINK}\s+${PROTOCOL}\s*$$ -> Record
